Using an example from the documentation verbatim, calling nwdiag-1.0.0 raises an error on [2U] expression in the nwdiag DSL:

```
#!text

&#37; nwdiag --version                    
nwdiag 1.0.0
```

```
#!text

&#37; cat simple-nwdiag.diag                               
rackdiag {
  // define height of rack
  16U;

  // define rack items
  1: UPS [2U];
  3: DB Server
  4: Web Server
  5: Web Server
  6: Web Server
  7: Load Balancer
  8: L3 Switch
}
```



